5D23006C.Line1.B79A2: Katherina? You mean Katherina Kressen? That old crone died when I was a child. More wrinkle than woman, they used to say! (laugh)

F71779EE.Line3.B79A2: She was burned and buried out back, under the memorial wall. Might be nice to stop by and pay respects. She don't get too many visitors.
